More at montblanc.com

Watch the second #MontblancSigned episode on IGTV or go to montblanc.com for more.

node.text:
We celebrated the launch of our latest collaboration by live
streaming with @matveimusic. Watch the full video at montblancxmaisonkitsune.com .

Created in Paris in 2002 by Gildas Loaëc and Masaya Kuroki, Kitsuné offers a unique Art de Vivre blending a fashion brand @maisonkitsune, music label @kitsunemusique and cafés, bars and restaurants @cafekitsune. “Kitsuné”, the Japanese word for “fox”, is a symbol of versatility that according to legend possesses the power to change its appearance. With this new collaboration, their next shape-shifting act is revealed. 
  
Shop the drop montblanc.com

node.text:
Thinking about founding a start-up?
We might have something for you: #RaisingTheStakes, the first episode of our new series #MontblancSigned.
A journey to the early days of a start-up you today might know under the name “Montblanc”.

Watch the first #MontblancSigned episode on IGTV or go to montblanc.com for more.

For @pawo_chen, acting is all about pushing boundaries, testing the limits and exploring the self. It's this same spirit of exploration that is reflected in our 1858 Geosphere collection.

An engraving of the Mont Blanc mountain, a compass, and two crossed ice pick-axes evoke the spirit of mountain exploration and the iconic peak that inspired the founders of the Maison. Tap to shop the Montblanc 1858 Geosphere UltraBlack Limited Edition.

@xin_zhilei's drive to push the boundaries of each new role she plays – always with determination and audacity – reflects our ethos: that everyone should be inspired to leave their mark. Our new Montblanc 1858 Geosphere UltraBlack also pushes the boundaries of what's expected. Wear it regardless of gender. Wear it during the day or at night. Wear it at the office or at home. 

Inspired by legendary professional Minerva watches, this timepiece features the Manufacture Worldtime complication with two turning domed hemisphere globes that make a full rotation in 24 hours. Tap to shop.

"We want to first solve the great mission that we have, which is to allow every child in Serbia to have access to early childhood education." — @djokernole

We’re proud to support his commitment to a cause that is also rooted in our own brand DNA. That’s why with every sale of this limited edition tote, funds will be donated to educational programs supported by the Novak Djokovic Foundation. #WhatMovesYouMakesYou
